CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 22, 1956, pg. A16 reads: "Feted - Mr. and Mrs. Wilford Allen received friends during a reception in their honor last Sunday at the Greene Hearth. The newlyweds were married Nov. 24.  The bride is the former Barbara Ann Goggin, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Leo Goggin.  - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Bride Barbara Ann Goggin Allen wearing satin gown and groom Wilford Allen, posed behind table with wrapped gifts in Greene Hearth
